name: Blackfire LoRA
description:
This is my Blackfire LoRA. This LoRA is trained on NovelAI, so it will not do particularly well with realistic models. It was also trained with a heavily NSFW dataset.

The strength is good from 0.6 to 0.8, but I use 0.75 strength. All images are generated are generated with Hires Fix and the Orangemix VAE. All pictures were made with the blends available on my profile.

The main keyword is 'blackfire'. Additionally, other tags beginning with 'black' and 'purple' will help push it in the right direction. (i.e. 'black hair' or 'purple eyes', etc.) 'Long hair' and 'parted bangs' also helps.

I also have a Discord. Join if you wanna share results, get advice, or make requests.
